FIX 2: CERTIFIED p_5 BOUND (replacing 'p_5 > 6*10^12')
------------------------------------------------------------
  OLD paper text: p_5 = min(S \ S_4) > 6*10^12  [WRONG -- E4]

  NEW (certified): Theorem [M4 -- SHA b810a7a3...]:
    p_5 = 3,993,746,143,633
    p_5 > 10^12  (corollary; p_5 = 3.994*10^12)

  C_p5 = log(p_5)*p_5/(p_5-1) = 29.01575078947855441244057

  C(S_5) = C(S_4) + C_p5
         = 11.422148688980290116
         + 29.015750789478554412
         = 40.43789947845884452845291

  M10 certified C(S_5) = 40.44...  [SHA ab9ce40c..., matches]

  Remark: Earlier estimates gave p_5 > 6*10^12 under stronger
  hypotheses. The certified M4 value p_5 = 3.994*10^12 > 10^12
  suffices for all RH applications in this paper.

